original: Lindgren, Egon FlHp Gustav, överlärare, Skänninge, f. 1/5/92 i Norrkö- ping av ibyggmäst. Harald L. o. Ad-frida Ramstedt. G. 20 m. Sigrid Molin. Barn: Britta f. 21, Märta 22, Margareta 29. — Folkskollär :ex. 14. Folkskollär. i Skänninge sed. 14, överlär. där sed. 35.
translated: Lindgren, Egon FlHp Gustav, headmaster, Skänninge, born 1/5/92 in Norrköping, son of construction master Harald L. and Ad-frida Ramstedt. Married in 1920 to Sigrid Molin. Children: Britta, born in 1921, Märta in 1922, Margareta in 1929. Graduated as a primary school teacher in 1914. Worked as a primary school teacher in Skänninge since 1914, promoted to headmaster in 1935.
